metadata.description: Welcome to Enchanted Creatures Club! We are a group of young artists who are passionate about preserving and restoring the delicate ecosystem of the Galapagos Islands. Our NFT collection features a variety of beautiful and endemic creatures that live in the islands, as a free mint 70% of the royalties will be donated to NGOs that work to protect the islands. Our partnership are with the Charles Darwin Foundation ensures that our project is sustainable and impactful. Join our community and own a piece of the unique and enchanting wildlife of the Galapagos Islands.
